"puede ejecutarse exponencialmente mÃĄs rÃĄpido en un ordenador cuÃĄntico que "
"los mejores algoritmos clÃĄsicos conocidos."

#: ../../tutorials/introductions/intro_quantum.rst:23
msgid ""
"Quantum advantage has been demonstrated for certain specific problems, "
"but it is still an open question as to how broadly it can be applied. It "
