#: ../../tutorials/introductions/intro_quantum.rst:27
msgid ""
"There is also the consideration that quantum computers tend to be more "
"energy-efficient than classical computers, at least in the theoretical "
"limit, so even if they don't provide a speed advantage for a particular "
"problem, they may still be advantageous in terms of energy consumption."
